{"tid":203681,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈推薦近期西班牙懸疑片《佈局/看不見的客人》","createTime":"2017-04-16T12:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T12:45:24.000Z","uid":944,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26b78e291b01a727ffd6c7fd4135f453d458d8d0","tid":203681,"uid":944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T12:50:19.000Z","msg":"《佈局 (台) / Contratiempo》(The Invisible Guest)【2016】(5/5)<br />\n國家：西班牙<br />\n導演：Oriol Paulo <br />\n主演：Mario Casas / Ana Wagener / Jos&eacute; Coronado / B&aacute;rbara Lennie / Francesc Orella<br />\n類型：劇情 / 懸疑 / 犯罪<br />\n片長：106分鐘<br />\n<br />\n超級強烈推薦的犯罪懸疑片！《佈局》由之前推介的《屍物招領》的導演Oriol Paulo執導，imdb7.8分，豆瓣8.7分，是小弟期待已久的他的新作！因為實在來不及等香港的發行商，所以用自己的方法率先看了，hehe。<br />\n<br />\n電影由一樁密室殺人案說起。全片的佈局嚴謹慎密，處處埋下伏筆，且總能自圓其說，幾乎沒有瑕疵，完成度甚高，對比導演前作《屍》更高章、更精彩！即使觀眾能猜到結局，但絕對不會猜到故事的全部。這並不只是一部傳統的結局大反轉電影，也不是那種一口氣解釋反轉的來龍去脈的片子。《佈局》是從頭到尾都能給你驚喜，層層遞進，反轉連連的電影，讓人有種坐過山車的快感。另外，電影的敘事結構也相當出色，有點《羅生門》的影子，讓觀眾游走在虛實之間，參與感十分強。觀看這類懸疑片一般都說不出什麼大道理，小弟只能說片子道出人性的黑暗面真的很黑......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gOTmQQUEcxU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgOTmQQUEcxU&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=7685bcc2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gOTmQQUEcxU</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/16/204954_75119c3e780efafd5479de00c4dbf6d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F16%2F204954_75119c3e780efafd5479de00c4dbf6d2.jpg&h=66567629&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e864668047bd170ce6b71a8771fecab55be484a","tid":203681,"uid":944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T12:58:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a02b7033e4aff7e0d30a52394e3522b944b4